messages.messageBody: Morning, Just waiting for a couple questions to get answered then we'll make a decision

You know what, I'm so sorry, somebody called me yesterday evening when I was working out and I totally forgot to call them back, I believe his name was Travis. Totally my bad! 

This power outage and 4 kids home from school has our household all turned upside down. 
Please have him call me today if he still needs me.
